ORR-ROOT-ADDRESS - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-ipv4-bgp-oper:bgp/config-instances/config-instance/{instance-name}/config-vrfs/config-vrf/{vrf-name}/entity-configurations/entity-configuration/af-dependent-config/orr-root-address/

Retrieve operation of resource: orr-root-address

instance-name: string
in path

ID of instance-name

vrf-name: string
in path

ID of vrf-name

200 OK
orr-root-address_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json
Response Example (200 OK)
